messages.content: Yes, I need the police at 963 East 36th Street.
Okay, give me the address again.
And you said it's a house?
And you said there's somebody in the house?
No, I'm not. I just got back from the store.
Are you the owner? What is your name?
No, I'm the grandson of the owner. She's in the house.
The owner is in the house?
My grandmother, yes. I live with her. I went to the store and there's somebody in the house.
Did you see them, hear them? Did she call you? What's going on?
No, I looked in the front door because all the doors were open, which isn't normal. And I could see her...
